6552 - Land Subdividers and Developers, Except Cemeteries Summary > POLY (AUSTRALIA) REAL ESTATE DEVELOPMENT PTY LIMITED (formerly EPPING 048 REAL ESTATE DEVELOPMENT PTY. LTD.) is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover land subdividers and developers, except cemeteries. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. POLY (AUSTRALIA) REAL ESTATE DEVELOPMENT PTY LIMITED is headquartered in Sydney, New South Wales. It is headed by director Yingnan Wang. For the 2023 financial year, the company reported revenue of $33.94 million. Its net loss totalled $94.22 million. POLY (AUSTRALIA) REAL ESTATE DEVELOPMENT PTY LIMITED forms part of the finance, insurance, and real estate industry sector.
